OL,5, A trustee of the charity Mermaids has  
OL,6, resigned after reports he spoke at a   
OL,7, conference organised by a group that   
OL,8, promotes support for paedophiles.      
OL,10,FDr Jacob Breslow quit the transgender  
OL,11,Fchildren's charity after the Times     
OL,12,Frevealed he had attended the B4U-ACT   
OL,13,Fconference in 2011, as a PhD student.  
OL,15,FB4U-ACT calls for paedophiles to have  
OL,16,Fthe right to live "in truth and        
OL,17,Fdignity".                              
OL,19,FMermaids says the organisation is      
OL,20,F"completely at odds" with its values.  
